by each carâ€™s CCU to broadcast messages over the car. </para><para reuse="all">Three types of Public Address loudspeakers are
used on the car (see Figure <ref-container><iref ref-id="BCEFDFJC"></iref></ref-container>): </para><list type="bulleted" reuse="all"><list-item><para reuse="all">Interior,
