for Automatic Output Level Adjustment.(AOLA), transformer, and power
taps. This speaker unit weighs 5 lb and measures approximately
11.0 in. wide, 7.6 in. height, and 4.0 in.
deep. The speaker body and removable face plate are painted steel.
The face plate is pierced to provide a protection grille for the speaker
cone and an opening for the microphone. </para></list-item><list-item><para reuse="all">Interior loudspeaker assembly, with
transformer and power taps. This speaker unit weighs 5 lb
and measures approximately 11.0 in. wide, 7.6 in.
height, and 4.0 in. deep. The speaker body and removable
face plate are painted steel. The face plate is pierced to provide
a protection grille for the speaker cone. </para></list-item><list-item><para reuse="all">Exterior loudspeaker assembly, with
transformer and power taps. This speaker unit weighs 5 lb
and measures approximately 8.5 in. wide, 6.5 in.
diameter, and 4.0 in. deep. The removable face plate is
stainless-steel and is pierced to provide a protection grille for
the speaker cone. </para></list-item></list><illustration reuse="all"><graphic file="..\..\Graphics\CGM\053J-751-016.cgm" cropped="1" float="0" height="5.70in" impsize="9.00in 5.70in"></graphic><title id="BCEFDFJC">PA Speakers</title></illustration><para reuse="all">The PA loudspeakers are distributed throughout
